Package nucleus

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Analysis
    The class Analysis contains all the information for defining an analysis for the system
    AnalysisList
    Class that manages all analysis in an ArrayList
    Date
    Class that defines and manages dates
    Employee
    Class that defines and manages an employee
    EmployeeList
    Class for managing the employees in a list
    FileIO
    Class for writing and reading from a file(.bin)
    Settings
    Class for changing the default graphic settings of the software
    SystemAdapterAnalysis
    Class for providing a cohesion between the FileIO class and the Analysis List Class
    SystemAdapterEmployee
    Class for providing a cohesion between the FileIO class and the Employee List Class
    SystemAdapterWeek
    Class for providing a cohesion between the FileIO class and the Week List Class
    SystemSEP
    Class for providing a unity for the week, analysis and employee lists
    Task
    Class for defining and managing a task
    TaskList
    Class for managing the tasks
    Training
    A class that manages an employee's training
    Vacation
    A class that sets up the Vacation for an Employee
    WeekList
    Class that manages task lists (6 task lists for 6 working days)
